  "text": "T were summed feature 3 (C 16 : 1 !7c, iso-C 15 : 0 2-OH; 65.8 %) and iso-C 15 : 0 (34.2 %), as characteristic for the genus Mucilaginibacter [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Fatty acid profiles of the novel strain and the closest related type strains are listed in Table 2 .",
  "correct_citation": {
